# Level 2 – Task 2: Tribute Page

## Project Title
Tribute Page for Dr. A. P. J. Abdul Kalam

## Objective
The objective of this project is to create a simple tribute webpage dedicated to Dr. A. P. J. Abdul Kalam, the former President of India and a great scientist.

## Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS

## Description
This project is a tribute webpage designed to honor Dr. A. P. J. Abdul Kalam, popularly known as the "Missile Man of India". The webpage highlights his achievements, contributions to science, and his inspirational life journey.

## Features
- Simple and clean webpage design
- Information about Dr. A. P. J. Abdul Kalam
- Structured layout using HTML and CSS
- Inspirational tribute content

